      "id": "PopularPost170870",
      "post_content": "I don't think it's that costly, considering blue has always been limited in how it can directly remove creatures that it couldn't counter. Just ![3](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=3&type=symbol) and tap the Assassin. Sure, [Royal Assassin](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Royal Assassin) or [Norritt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Norritt) with [Icy Manipulator](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Icy Manipulator) can bring the same result for ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol) but that's black-based and creature removal is a dime a dozen in black.  \n  \nGood oldschool combo, and on its own it's decent sideboard against blue in the worst case. It can also combo with [Reef Shaman](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Reef Shaman) or something else that turns someone else's land into an island.",
      "posted_by": "jfre81",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost170870\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">I don't think it's that costly, considering blue has always been limited in how it can directly remove creatures that it couldn't counter. Just <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"3\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=3&amp;type=symbol\"/> and tap the Assassin. Sure, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Royal Assassin\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Royal Assassin\">Royal Assassin</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Norritt\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Norritt\">Norritt</a> with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Icy Manipulator\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Icy Manipulator\">Icy Manipulator</a> can bring the same result for <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"1\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=1&amp;type=symbol\"/> but that's black-based and creature removal is a dime a dozen in black.<br/><br/>Good oldschool combo, and on its own it's decent sideboard against blue in the worst case. It can also combo with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Reef Shaman\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Reef Shaman\">Reef Shaman</a> or something else that turns someone else's land into an island.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '170870'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedB